CONTRIBUTING
============

Thanks for the contribution to the wiki!
We do not want to enforce strict policies,
these are merely etiquettes for commiting
to the wiki.

Commit messages
---------------

Your commit message should be in the following 
format:

        <subject>: <short description>


An example could be:

	wireless: configuring wpa_supplicant


Site structure
--------------

The wiki should be formed in a parent-child 
structure.
Example:


			      -- iwd
                             |
	       -- wireless -- -- index.md
              |              |
networking --- -- index.md    -- wpa_supplicant
              |
	      |
	       -- ethernet -- index.md
                             |
	                      -- an article on some ethernet adapter
